## LLM / AI Integration Options

### Option A: OpenAI API (Recommended for MVP Demo)
- **Cost**: Paid usage (~$0.01–0.10 per request for GPT-4 mini or GPT-3.5 Turbo)
- **Free Trial**: $5 credit included (enough for 1000s of test requests)
- **Freedom to Use**: ✅ **Fully allowed** for nonprofit projects; no restriction on output
- **Note**: You pay only for what you use; excellent for prototyping

### Option B: Open-Source Models (Llama 2, Mistral)
- **License**: Llama 2 Community License (allows commercial and nonprofit use)
- **Freedom to Use**: ✅ **Completely free** to download and run locally
- **Cost**: $0 (you host it yourself on your hardware or free cloud tier)
- **Hosting Options**:
  - Local machine (if you have GPU)
  - Hugging Face Inference API (free tier available)
  - Replicate ($.0005 per second, roughly $0.02–0.10 per request)

### Option C: Hugging Face API
- **License**: Various (most models are open-source friendly)
- **Cost**: Free tier available for inference
- **Freedom to Use**: ✅ **Fully allowed**
- **Note**: Great for testing without spending money; sufficient for demo

### Option D: Anthropic's Claude API
- **Cost**: Paid usage (~$0.005–0.03 per request)
- **Free Trial**: $5 credit
- **Freedom to Use**: ✅ **Fully allowed** for nonprofit projects

**Recommendation for MVP**: Start with OpenAI API ($5 free trial) or Hugging Face free tier. Both are fully unrestricted for nonprofit use and will keep costs near $0 during prototyping.

